(1, 10, 15, '73e671958c872be3bbe79d770e53e8fc1d0d2624.png', 'Ahmed Al-Farsi', 'Business Consultant', 'FFF5F5', 5, 'I’ve been a regular shopper here for months, and I am never disappointed. The quality of the fresh produce and meats is always top-notch, and the prices are very reasonable. The staff is incredibly helpful and friendly.', '2024-11-14 09:27:42', '2024-11-14 09:29:33'),
