(4, 10, 15, '512e2ee67a9c440cab329bc3a9c885eb6caa164b.png', 'Faisal Al-Mansoori', 'IT Specialist', 'FAF5FF', 4, 'Good prices and a great selection of products. I always find what I need, but I wish there were more variety in the snacks section. Overall, I’m very satisfied with the quality and service.', '2024-11-14 09:33:19', '2024-11-14 09:33:19'),
