(11, 10, 6, NULL, 15, 79, 63, 'Fresh & Sweet Pineapple – Tropical Delight in Every Bite', 'fresh---sweet-pineapple-–-tropical-delight-in-every-bite', 'Our fresh pineapples are a tropical treat, bursting with natural sweetness and tang. Perfect for snacking, adding to smoothies, or topping off desserts, these juicy pineapples are an irresistible way to indulge in a healthy, refreshing snack.', '<p>Delight in the tropical goodness of our <strong>fresh pineapples</strong>—handpicked at the peak of ripeness to ensure the perfect balance of sweetness and tanginess. Known for their juicy, vibrant flesh and aromatic scent, these pineapples bring a refreshing burst of flavor to any dish.</p>\r\n<p>Packed with <strong>vitamins</strong> and <strong>antioxidants</strong>, pineapples are not only delicious but also offer great health benefits. Rich in <strong>vitamin C</strong>, they boost your immune system, aid digestion, and provide a natural energy boost. Whether eaten fresh, blended into smoothies, or used in savory or sweet dishes, our pineapples offer endless culinary possibilities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Pineapples?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Naturally Sweet &amp; Tangy:</strong> Enjoy the perfect balance of sweetness and tartness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Loaded with Vitamin C:</strong> A natural way to boost your immune system and enhance overall health.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile &amp; Delicious:</strong> Perfect for eating fresh, juicing, smoothies, salads, or tropical desserts.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Handpicked &amp; Fresh:</strong> Carefully selected to ensure top-quality and freshness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Healthy &amp; Nutritious:</strong> Packed with antioxidants, enzymes, and vitamins to support a healthy lifestyle.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Sweet:</strong> Our pineapples are handpicked at the peak of ripeness, ensuring juicy, sweet flesh.</li>\r\n<li><strong>High in Vitamin C:<