(15, 10, 8, NULL, 15, 79, 59, 'Fresh, Crisp Apples – Sweet, Juicy, and Refreshing', 'fresh,-crisp-apples-–-sweet,-juicy,-and-refreshing', 'Our fresh apples are the perfect balance of sweet and crisp, offering a refreshing snack with every bite. Ideal for enjoying fresh, adding to salads, or baking into delicious pies, these apples are sure to delight.', '<p>Experience the crispness and sweetness of our <strong>fresh apples</strong>, handpicked from the best orchards for the perfect balance of flavor and texture. Known for their bright, juicy flesh and refreshing crunch, these apples are a delicious and healthy treat that can be enjoyed year-round.</p>\r\n<p>Packed with <strong>vitamins</strong> and <strong>fiber</strong>, apples are a nutritious snack that supports digestive health and provides a natural energy boost. Whether you prefer them sliced in a salad, baked into a pie, or enjoyed as a quick snack, these apples are incredibly versatile.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Apples?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Sweet &amp; Crisp:</strong> Enjoy the perfect balance of sweetness and crunch in every bite.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rich in Fiber:</strong> A great source of dietary fiber to support digestive health.</li>\r\n<li><strong>High in Vitamins:</strong> Packed with essential vitamins, especially vitamin C, for a natural immune boost.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Perfect for fresh snacking, baking, juicing, or adding to salads.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Juicy:</strong> Handpicked for maximum flavor and juiciness, ensuring the highest quality.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Crisp &amp; Refreshing:</strong> Each apple is selected for its firm texture and satisfying crunch.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Nutrient-Rich:</strong> Loaded with vitamins, antioxidants, and fiber for a healthy snack.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile &amp; Delicious:</strong> Perfect for a variety of uses – from snacking to baking and smoothies.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Freshly Harvested:</strong> Sourced from trusted orchards and picked at the peak of ripeness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Healthy &amp; Natural:</strong> A low-calorie, fiber-packed fruit that promotes digestion and boosts energy.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'fresh apples, crisp apples, sweet apples, apples for snacking, juicy apples, healthy apples, apples for baking, apples for pies, vitamin C, fiber-rich apples, organic apples', 'Shop fresh apples packed with sweetness and crispness. Perfect for snacking, baking, and adding to salads. Our handpicked apples are juicy, nutritious, and ready to enjoy. Get yours today!', '2024-11-13 09:11:32', '2024-11-13 09:11:32'),
(16, 10, 8, NULL, 16, 80, 60, 'تفاح طازج ومقرمش – حلو وعصيري ومنعش', 'تفاح-طازج-ومقرمش-–-حلو-وعصيري-ومنعش', 'تفاحنا الطازج هو التوازن المثالي بين الحلاوة والمقرمشة، ويقدم لك وجبة خفيفة منعشة في كل قضمة. مثالي للتناول الطازج، أو إضافته إلى السلطات، أو تحضيره في فطائر لذيذة، هذا التفاح سيسعد ذوقك.', '<p>استمتع <strong>بتفاحنا الطازج</strong> المقرمش والحلو، الذي يتم قطفه يدويًا من أفضل المزارع لضمان التوازن المثالي بين النكهة والقوام. يتميز هذا التفاح بلونه الزاهي والعصيري وقرمشته اللذيذة، مما يجعله معاملة لذيذة وصحية يمكنك الاستمتاع بها طوال العام.</p>\r\n<p>غني بـ <strong>الفيتامينات</strong> و <strong>الألياف</strong>، يعد التفاح وجبة خفيفة مغذية تدعم صحة الجهاز الهضمي وتوفر طاقة طبيعية. سواء كنت تفضله مقطعًا في السلطة، أو مخبوزًا في فطائر لذيذة، أو تناولته كوجبة خفيفة سريعة، فإن هذا التفاح متعدد الاستخدامات للغاية.</p>\r\n<p><strong>لماذا تختار تفاحنا الطازج؟</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>حلو ومقرمش:</strong> استمتع بالتوازن المثالي بين الحلاوة والقرمشة في كل قضمة.</li>\r\n<li><strong>غني بالألياف:</strong> مصدر رائع للألياف الغذائية التي تدعم صحة الجهاز الهضمي.</li>\r\n<li><strong>غني بالفيتامينات:</strong> يحتوي على فيتامينات أساسية، خاصة فيتامين C، لتعزيز جهاز المناعة.</li>\r\n<li><strong>متعدد الاستخدامات:</strong> مثالي للتناول الطازج، أو الخبز، أو العصير، أو إضافته إلى السلطات.</li>\r\n<li><strong>طازج وعصيري:</strong> يتم قطفه يدويًا لضمان أفضل طعم وعصارة، مما يضمن أعلى جودة.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>المزايا الرئيسية:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>مقرمش ومنعش:</strong> يتم اختيار كل حبة تفاح لتكون ذات قوام متماسك وقرمشة مرضية.</li>\r\n<li><strong>غني بالفيتامينات:</strong> مليء بالفيتامينات، ومضادات الأكسدة، والألياف كوجبة خفيفة صحية.</li>\r\n<li><strong>متعدد الاستخدامات:</strong> مثالي لمجموعة متنوعة من الاستخدامات – من الوجبات الخفيفة إلى الخبز والعصائر.</li>\r\n<li><strong>موسم الحصاد الطازج:</strong> يأتي من مزارع موثوقة ويتم قطافه في الوقت المثالي لضمان أفضل نكهة وجودة.</li>\r\n<li><strong>صحي وطبيعي:</strong> فاكهة منخفضة السعرات الحرارية ومليئة بالألياف التي تدعم الهضم وتزيد الطاقة.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, '2024-11-13 09:11:32', '2024-11-13 09:11:32'),
(17, 10, 9, NULL, 15, 79, 57, 'Fresh & Ripe Bananas – Naturally Sweet, Healthy & Delicious', 'fresh---ripe-bananas-–-naturally-sweet,-healthy---delicious', 'Our fresh bananas are naturally sweet, creamy, and packed with nutrients. Perfect for a quick snack, blending into smoothies, or adding to baked goods, these bananas are a healthy and delicious choice for any occasion.', '<p>Indulge in the goodness of <strong>fresh bananas</strong>—the perfect combination of natural sweetness, creaminess, and nutrition. Sourced from the finest farms, our bananas are handpicked at the peak of ripeness to ensure maximum flavor and texture. With their rich yellow color and smooth texture, these bananas are not only visually appealing but also offer a satisfying, delicious bite.</p>\r\n<p>Bananas are an excellent source of <strong>potassium</strong>, which supports heart health and muscle function, as well as <strong>vitamins</strong> and <strong>fiber</strong> that contribute to overall well-being. Whether you eat them on their own, add them to smoothies, or use them in baking recipes, bananas are a versatile and healthy addition to your diet.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Bananas?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Naturally Sweet &amp; Creamy:</strong> Enjoy the perfect combination of sweetness and creaminess in every bite.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rich in Potassium:</strong> Supports heart health, muscle function, and overall energy levels.</li>\r\n<li><strong>High in Fiber:</strong> Promotes healthy digestion and helps maintain a balanced diet.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Ideal for snacking, smoothies, baking, or as a topping for cereal and yogurt.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Ripe:</strong> Handpicked for maximum freshness and flavor, ensuring the best quality.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Naturally Sweet:</strong> A delicious snack packed with natural sugars that satisfy your sweet cravings.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Loaded with Potassium:</strong> A heart-healthy fruit that helps regulate blood pressure and supports muscle function.</li>\r\n<li><strong>High in Fiber:</strong> Supports digestive health and helps you feel fuller longer.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Freshly Picked:</strong> Sourced from trusted farms and harvested at the perfect time for ripeness and flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Energy Boosting:</strong> Provides a quick and natural energy boost, making it the perfect pre- or post-workout snack.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'fresh bananas, ripe bananas, sweet bananas, bananas for smoothies, potassium-rich bananas, healthy bananas, bananas for snacking, bananas for baking, fiber-rich bananas, organic bananas', 'Shop fresh bananas that are naturally sweet, creamy, and packed with potassium. Perfect for snacking, smoothies, and baking. Handpicked for freshness and flavor. Get yours today!', '2024-11-13 09:18:00', '2024-11-13 09:18:00');
