(251, 15, 126, NULL, 25, 171, 279, 'Ultra-Slim 15.6\" Intel Core i7 Laptop with 16GB RAM', 'ultra-slim-15.6\"-intel-core-i7-laptop-with-16gb-ram', 'A high-performance ultra-slim laptop featuring a powerful Intel Core i7 processor, 16GB RAM, and a stunning 15.6\" display. Ideal for professionals, students, and creators on the go.', '<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<p>Experience seamless performance and portability with our Ultra-Slim 15.6\" Intel Core i7 Laptop. Designed for multitasking, this sleek powerhouse features a 10th Gen Intel Core i7 processor and 16GB of RAM, ensuring smooth performance for demanding applications, gaming, or creative projects. The vibrant 15.6\" Full HD display delivers stunning visuals, while the solid-state drive (SSD) provides lightning-fast boot times and ample storage for