(43, 24, 14, 50, 96, 'Remote-Controlled Toy Truck – Adventure on Wheels', '7954277', 1, '149', '6744407665724.png', 'Fuel your child’s imagination with the Remote-Controlled Toy Truck! This exciting and durable truck brings hours of fun, allowing young drivers to experience the thrill of remote control action while navigating through their own mini adventures.', '<p>Get ready for an action-packed ride with the <em>Remote-Controlled Toy Truck</em>! Built for both indoor and outdoor play, this sturdy truck features an easy-to-use remote that lets your child steer, accelerate, and even perform stunts with just the push of a button. Whether it\'s racing across the living room or conquering the backyard, this truck offers the perfect balance of fun and adventure.</p>\r\n<p>The toy truck is designed for children aged 3 and up and comes with a robust build to handle bumps and falls. With large wheels, it effortlessly glides over various terrains, allowing your child to explore different environments and create exciting races or obstacle courses.</p>\r\n<p>The intuitive remote controller is simple enough for younger children to use, providing both forward and backward movement, as well as a 360-degree turning radius. Its sleek design and vibrant colors make it a standout toy that will keep your child entertained for hours.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect as a birthday gift or a special treat, the Remote-Controlled Toy Truck is sure to be a hit with any young vehicle enthusiast!</p>', 39.99, 49.99, '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":348,\"name\":\"1:16 Scale\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":351,\"name\":\"Yellow\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:32:04', NULL),
