(114, 73, 10, 56, 19, 'Fresh Crisp Lettuce – Organic, Nutrient-Packed & Refreshing Green', '8916711', 3, '87', '67359d8c5e812.png', 'Fresh lettuce is a crisp and refreshing green that’s perfect for salads, sandwiches, wraps, and more. This organic variety is packed with vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants, making it a healthy and delicious choice for any meal. Enjoy the cool crunch and versatility of lettuce in all your favorite dishes.', '<p>Add a refreshing crunch to your meals with our <strong>Fresh Organic Lettuce</strong>. Known for its light, crisp texture and mild flavor, lettuce is an essential green that’s both versatile and healthy. Whether you\'re building a salad, layering it into a sandwich, or using it as a wrap for your favorite fillings, lettuce brings a crisp, hydrating element to any dish.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Lettuce?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Loaded with Nutrients:</strong> Lettuce is low in calories but rich in essential nutrients. It\'s an excellent source of vitamin K, which supports bone health, and vitamin A, which is important for eye health and immune function. Lettuce also contains folate, fiber, and a variety of minerals that promote overall well-being.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Hydrating and Refreshing:</strong> Lettuce is made up of over 90% water, making it one of the most hydrating vegetables available. It’s the perfect addition to summer salads, refreshing smoothies, or as a base for your healthy wraps and bowls.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile in the Kitchen:</strong> Whether you\'re tossing it into a fresh garden salad, using it as a crunchy topping for tacos, or wrapping it around grilled chicken for a healthy meal, lettuce is a versatile green that works with almost any dish. It adds both texture and a mild flavor that pairs well with a variety of ingredients.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Supports a Healthy Lifestyle:</strong> With its high water content, lettuce helps with digestion and promotes hydration, which is essential for maintaining healthy skin, regulating body temperature, and supporting overall health. It’s also low in calories, making it a great choice for anyone looking to maintain or lose weight.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Organic and Fresh:</strong> Grown without pesticides or harmful chemicals, our lettuce is harvested fresh from organic farms, ensuring you get the cleanest, most nutritious product available.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Add a head of <strong>Fresh Organic Lettuce</strong> to your cart today and enjoy its crisp, refreshing flavor and health benefits in every bite. Whether you\'re preparing a light salad or creating a filling meal, this lettuce will be the perfect addition.</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', 1.28, NULL, NULL, '2025-02-20 13:22:36', NULL),
(115, 74, 12, 58, 70, 'Adidas Ultraboost 22 Performance Gym Shoes', '6864024', 1, '119', '674165256c2a1.png', 'The Adidas Ultraboost 22 Performance Gym Shoes are engineered for maximum comfort and performance, featuring a responsive Boost midsole and breathable mesh upper. Perfect for both gym workouts and outdoor activities, these shoes provide the support and flexibility you need to stay at the top of your game.', '<p>The <strong>Adidas Ultraboost 22 Performance Gym Shoes</strong> are designed to help you perform at your best, no matter the workout. The signature Boost midsole technology offers superior cushioning and energy return with every step, providing a responsive feel that helps you power through intense sessions. The breathable mesh upper enhances airflow, keeping your feet cool and dry during even the toughest workouts.</p>\r\n<p>These shoes feature a durable rubber outsole with a grippy pattern, providing excellent traction on a variety of surfaces. Whether you\'re lifting, running, or doing agility drills, the <strong>Ultraboost 22</strong> ensures stability and support, giving you the confidence to push yourself further. The sleek, modern design with reflective details also adds a stylish touch, making these shoes perfect for both the gym and casual wear.</p>\r\n<p>Available in a range of colors, the <strong>Adidas Ultraboost 22 Gym Shoes</strong> combine performance with comfort and style, making them an essential addition to any fitness enthusiast\'s collection.</p>', 148.99, 259.99, '{\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":47,\"option_id\":121,\"name\":\"24.4 cm\",\"price\":12,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":48,\"option_id\":125,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":15,\"stock\":99}}', '2025-02-20 13:37:08', NULL),
(116, 74, 12, 58, 67, 'Men\'s Regular Fit Performance Sports Jersey for Active Wear and Everyday Comfort', '9716217', 1, '119', '674161f798422.png', 'The Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey offers the perfect balance of comfort and style. Made from soft, breathable fabric, it’s ideal for everyday wear, providing a relaxed fit and versatile look that pairs well with any casual outfit.', '<p>The <strong>Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey</strong> is designed for maximum comfort and effortless style. Made from high-quality cotton blend fabric, this jersey is soft to the touch and highly breathable, making it perfect for daily wear. The regular fit ensures a relaxed, non-restrictive feel that keeps you comfortable all day long, whether you’re running errands, lounging at home, or meeting friends.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a simple crew neckline and short sleeves, this jersey offers a clean, minimalist look that easily complements any wardrobe. Available in a variety of classic colors, it’s easy to pair with jeans, shorts, or casual trousers for a laid-back, stylish outfit. The lightweight fabric also makes it ideal for layering or wearing on its own during warmer weather.</p>\r\n<p>Durable and versatile, the <strong>Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey</strong> is a wardrobe essential for men who value comfort and simplicity without compromising on style. Whether you’re relaxing or out on the go, this jersey will be a go-to for all your casual outfits.</p>', 11.75, 39.99, '{\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":50,\"option_id\":130,\"name\":\"Xl\",\"price\":3,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":51,\"option_id\":134,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":99}}', '2025-02-20 13:37:08', NULL),
(117, 74, 12, 58, 65, 'Bigmo Club Premium Performance Football Jersey for Ultimate Comfort and Durability', '4062739', 1, '119', '67417335714cf.png', 'The Bigmo Club Football Jersey is a tribute to the legendary club’s legacy, combining traditional design with modern performance features. Whether you\'re cheering from the stands or playing on the pitch, this jersey is perfect for any Barça supporter.', '<p>The Bigmo Club Football Jersey blends the club’s iconic blaugrana stripes with cutting-edge performance technology. Made from lightweight, breathable fabric, this jersey is designed to keep you cool and comfortable during intense activities or casual wear. Featuring the classic FC Barcelona crest on the chest, it represents the pride, passion, and success of one of football\'s greatest clubs.</p>\r\n<p>The jersey\'s advanced moisture-wicking technology ensures you stay dry and comfortable, while the breathable mesh panels enhance ventilation and airflow. With a sleek, modern fit, the Bigmo Club Football Jersey allows for freedom of movement, making it perfect for both athletic performance and everyday wear.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re wearing it to show your support at Camp Nou or on your next football match, this jersey is a must-have for all true Barça fans. Celebrate the pride of the Catalan club with the Bigmo Club Football Jersey, and wear your passion on your sleeve.</p>', 599.99, 899.99, '{\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":53,\"option_id\":139,\"name\":\"Xl\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":54,\"option_id\":143,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":20,\"stock\":99}}', '2025-02-20 13:37:08', NULL),
(118, 74, 12, 58, 64, 'Men\'s Athletic Fit Training Jersey', '2670573', 1, '119', '6741736ee37bd.png', 'The Men\'s Dri-FIT Training Jersey offers superior comfort and performance, featuring moisture-wicking technology and a lightweight design. Perfect for workouts or casual wear, this jersey keeps you cool and dry while providing a stylish athletic look.', '<p>The <strong>Men\'s Dri-FIT Training Jersey</strong> is crafted to support you through intense workouts and everyday activities. Made from high-quality, moisture-wicking Dri-FIT fabric, it efficiently pulls sweat away from your skin, keeping you dry and comfortable. The lightweight material and relaxed fit allow for a full range of motion, making it ideal for training, sports, or casual wear.</p>\r\n<p>This jersey features a classic crew neck and short sleeves, ensuring a timeless, versatile style. The breathable design enhances airflow, preventing overheating during high-intensity exercises. The bold Nike Swoosh logo on the chest adds a sporty touch, giving you that authentic athletic look.</p>\r\n<p>Available in various colors, the <strong>Men\'s Dri-FIT Training Jersey</strong> is the perfect combination of functionality and style, making it a must-have addition to any fitness wardrobe. Whether you\'re on the field, in the gym, or out with friends, this jersey delivers the comfort and performance you need.</p>', 999.99, 1499.99, '{\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":55,\"option_id\":144,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":99},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":56,\"option_id\":149,\"name\":\"Blue\",\"price\":35,\"stock\":99}}', '2025-02-20 13:37:08', NULL),
