(145, 81, 14, 59, 101, 'Art & Craft Kits – Creative Fun for All Ages', '6563963', 1, '149', '674442abb6d41.png', 'Unleash your creativity with our Art & Craft Kits! Perfect for kids, beginners, or seasoned artists, these kits provide everything you need to craft beautiful, personalized projects and explore your artistic talents.', '<p>Dive into the world of creativity with our <em>Art &amp; Craft Kits</em>! Whether you\'re a budding artist or just looking for a fun, hands-on activity, these all-in-one kits are designed to inspire and engage. Packed with high-quality materials, each kit comes with everything you need to create stunning works of art—from paints and brushes to paper, beads, and more.</p>\r\n<p>Our kits are perfect for kids, teens, and adults alike, offering a variety of craft activities such as painting, drawing, jewelry-making, scrapbooking, and more. Each kit is carefully curated to ensure ease of use, with step-by-step instructions to guide you through each project.</p>\r\n<p>Not only are these Art &amp; Craft Kits an ideal way to spend quality time with family and friends, but they also promote essential skills like fine motor development, creativity, and problem-solving. These kits make excellent gifts for birthdays, holidays, or any occasion that calls for a creative touch.</p>\r\n<p>With a wide range of themes and projects, including seasonal crafts, DIY decorations, and personalized gift ideas, there’s a kit to suit every taste and occasion. Let your imagination run wild and create beautiful, one-of-a-kind pieces with our Art &amp; Craft Kits!</p>', 19.99, 24.99, '[]', '2025-02-25 04:43:30', NULL),
(146, 81, 14, 59, 104, 'School Backpack – Durable, Spacious, and Comfortable for Kids', '2809861', 1, '153', '674444aa7fa2f.png', 'Our Premium School Backpack is designed to meet the needs of active kids. With spacious compartments, padded straps, and durable materials, it’s the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality for school and everyday use.', '<p>Prepare your child for the school year with our <em>Premium School Backpack</em>! Built to withstand the rigors of daily use, this backpack combines style, durability, and comfort in one. Made from high-quality, water-resistant materials, it’s designed to keep books, notebooks, and school supplies safe and organized.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a spacious main compartment and additional pockets for smaller items, this backpack has plenty of room for everything your child needs for a day at school. From textbooks and stationery to lunch boxes and water bottles, everything has its place. The easy-to-access front pocket is perfect for storing pens, keys, or even a phone.</p>\r\n<p>Comfort is key with this backpack’s padded shoulder straps, which provide extra support and reduce pressure, making it easy for your child to carry their essentials without strain. The breathable back panel ensures airflow to keep your child comfortable, even during long days.</p>\r\n<p>With a fun, vibrant design, this backpack is sure to brighten up your child\'s school day. Whether they\'re in elementary school or high school, this versatile backpack is an ideal choice for students of all ages. Available in multiple colors and patterns, there\'s a style to suit every personality.</p>', 52.79, 89.99, '{\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":148,\"option_id\":356,\"name\":\"Navy Blue\",\"price\":\"10.00\",\"stock\":100},\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":149,\"option_id\":359,\"name\":\"Medium\",\"price\":\"20.00\",\"stock\":100}}', '2025-02-25 04:43:30', NULL),
